title: Google\Cloud\AIPlatform\V1\ExportFeatureValuesRequest\FullExport
name: FullExport
description:
Describes exporting all historical Feature values of all entities of the EntityType between [start_time, end_time].

Generated from protobuf message google.cloud.aiplatform.v1.ExportFeatureValuesRequest.FullExport

params.name: data

params.name: data.start_time
params.description: Excludes Feature values with feature generation timestamp before this timestamp. If not set, retrieve oldest values kept in Feature Store. Timestamp, if present, must not have higher than millisecond precision.
